verbose_text: Although no SSC specific marker has been identified, whole-mount analyses indicate that GFRalpha1, PLZF, CDH1 and OCT3/4 are expressed by undifferentiated spermatogonia, including A single, A paired and A aligned (clones of 4-16 cells) spermatogonia.
evidence: GFRalpha1, PLZF, CDH1 and OCT3/4 are expressed
